Created by SatanTheSith.
Some Ideas for the map to expand it were from Refoops and OOPman, who are not members of fpsbanana as of now.

There are LOTS of invisible platforms (some to get to the top of the roof). If you climb the red metal peices there is an invisible wall so people can only shoot you if they are climbing it too. There are secret ladders and invisible platforms to teleport to other spawn, but they are hard to find. Have fun!

Great for deathmatch or gungame.
